INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES('15', '1', '2014-05-26 11:09:39', '2014-05-26 11:09:39', 'Message from the Head of Department\r\n\r\nA Message from the Head of Department\r\n\r\nJanuary 2014\r\n\r\nI wish to extend a warm welcome to all who have come to visit this website of the Pharmacy Department located at the National University of Singapore. As we step into a brand new year, I like to take this opportunity to wish you a successful and rewarding year in 2014.\r\nThe Department remains as the only academic unit in a university that offers a professional Pharmacy education that leads to registration as pharmacists in Singapore. Therefore its vision is to become a leader in shaping healthcare through innovative pharmaceutical education, research and practice.\r\nAs a Department, we are aspired to shape the local healthcare landscape and to be an active citizen in the global healthcare arena by\r\n\r\nproviding world class pharmaceutical education through innovative teaching pedagogies which prepare our graduates to be competent pharmacists and creative pharmaceutical scientists who can transform the lives of patients.\r\n\r\nengaging in cutting edge pharmaceutical research leading to new discovery in drug therapy and new practices for better health outcomes.\r\n\r\ninfluencing changes in health services that bring about better cost effective treatments and lower drug related problems.\r\n\r\nThe Department is made up of a group of dedicated staff members who share common core values that bring us together as a “Pharmily” (a term of endearment which we hold close to our hearts). We believe that these core values are essentially embedded in all pharmacists and pharmaceutical scientists and we aim to be able to impart these values to our all students. Therefore,\r\n\r\nwe are dedicated and committed to serve our students and patients so that they can receive the best outcomes from what we do for them.\r\n\r\nwe aim to act in ways that are professional and ethical so that we gain respect and trust from all those with whom we interact.\r\n\r\nwe aim to lead and do our best to achieve excellence in whatever we do.\r\n\r\nwe aim to be progressive in our development so that we can provide the best by using innovations in our education, research and practice.\r\n\r\nwe aim to work as a team to overcome adversities; and create a vibrant and collegial environment for all.\r\n\r\nThe values are put together to form the word “PHARMACY” to demonstrate that these values are embraced in the profession and that upholding these values is our priority in the Department. As we re-affirm our dedications to the Pharmacy profession at the beginning of the New Year, we look forward to an exciting and successful year ahead.', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2014-07-12 14:45:11', '2014-07-12 14:45:11', '', '0', 'http://www.nstupharma.org/?page_id=15', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES('17', '1', '2014-05-26 11:09:53', '2014-05-26 11:09:53', '<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n          .entry-title{display:none}\r\n         </style>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Welcome to NSTU Pharma Family!</span></h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This web portal is launched with a view to maintain a collaboration with its honorable teachers, regular students, alumni, pharmaceutical industries, Govt. regulatory bodies and prospective students who are interested in pursuing a career in pharmacy and related areas. The department offers four-year Bachelor of pharmacy degree and Post-Graduation in ‘Clinical Pharmacy and Pharmacology’.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Noakhali Science and Technology University (NSTU) that popularly known as ‘Coastal University’ was established on March 24, 2005 and started its academic activities on June 22, 2006 with only four departments that today rose to fourteen departments. Among those departments Pharmacy is one of high priority choice to students coming for university education. Since its inception, our department along with ‘Parma family’ members have been struggling to prepare ‘Quality Pharmacists’ through generating and disseminating knowledge among students who are supposed to contribute their best in Healthcare systems and will prove their excellence.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">On our web portal, prospective students can learn more about our academic programs, financial aid and the application process. For our alumni, the site will keep you abreast of various alumni events as well as our extensive continuing education offerings for practicing pharmacists.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thank you for visiting us.</p>', 'Welcome', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'welcome', '', '', '2014-07-15 05:06:22', '2014-07-15 05:06:22', '', '15', 'http://www.nstupharma.org/?page_id=17', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES('19', '1', '2014-05-26 11:10:25', '2014-05-26 11:10:25', 'Pharmacists are called ‘medications expert’. With the development of medical science, the importance of pharmacy education is reasonably increasing to ensure proper health safety. Today, pharmacy is of high priority choice that covers high prestigious profession. We have managed our destination bearing the theme ‘we are for humanity’ and walking to our own designed way to make an uncountable patients smile.\r\n\r\nOur mission is to prepare pharmacists to provide optimal pharmaceutical care, and to prepare graduate and postgraduate students for leadership in teaching, research, practice and service. The department generates and disseminates knowledge to promote safe, clinically effective, and cost-efficient use of medications. Thus being an integral member of the healthcare team responsible for the outcomes associated with the medication use process.\r\n\r\nOur Vision is to be recognized nationally and internationally as an absolute leader in pharmacy education and research that focuses on appropriate use of and access to pharmaceuticals and medical devices, as well as cost-effective provision and delivery of pharmaceutical care.\r\n\r\nAs a part and to materialize our vision we have undertaken the following goals:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Recognizing that the pharmacists are our most important resource.</li>\r\n	<li>Contributing to and accepting responsibility for optimal therapeutic outcomes including promoting wellness.</li>\r\n	<li>Fostering an environment that promotes the safe, efficacious, and cost-effective use of medications.</li>\r\n	<li>Improving the medication use process to enhance continuity of care.</li>\r\n	<li>Making sound decisions supported by evidence based medicine through research on medication use and patient safety.</li>\r\n	<li>Developing and conducting research to improve the safety and efficiency of the medication use system.</li>\r\n	<li>Utilizing research methods to identify the most cost effective use of medications.</li>\r\n	<li>Initiating and supporting interdisciplinary collaborative research.</li>\r\n	<li>To improve patient outcomes and provide the highest standards of pharmaceutical care.</li>\r\n	<li>To promote research to improve patient outcomes and the efficiency of care.</li>\r\n	<li>To expand and promote excellence in pharmacy education.</li>\r\n	<li>To build up an ideal person, combining morality with professionalism.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn fine, we are hopeful of our success in the way to our destination.\r\n\r\nLast but not the least, we believe to be a good Person first as well as a good Pharmacist.', 'Vission & Mission', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vission-mission', '', '', '2014-07-12 14:48:25', '2014-07-12 14:48:25', '', '15', 'http://www.nstupharma.org/?page_id=19', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES('21', '1', '2014-05-26 11:10:49', '2014-05-26 11:10:49', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://www.nstupharma.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/10526620_10202393226494391_1185314775_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-415\" src=\"http://www.nstupharma.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/10526620_10202393226494391_1185314775_n.jpg\" alt=\"10526620_10202393226494391_1185314775_n\" width=\"164\" height=\"205\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hello Visitors/ Aspirants,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welcome to the website of the Department of Pharmacy of Noakhali Science and Technology University (NSTU). The University is one of the highly credited grounds for Pharmacy education in the southern terrain of the country. This department is accredited by Bangladesh Pharmacy Council (BPC).  We have launched this web portal with a view to strengthen our mutual communication and to make you informed of our programs and curriculum, who are interested in pursuing a career in Pharmacy and other related areas and also others, who are keen to keep them abreast of our departmental events.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Since our inception, we are committed to provide a quality education to meet the demand of the twenty-first century. It’s my pleasure to inform you; here we offer four-year Bachelor of Pharmacy (B.Pharm) degree and also Master of Pharmacy (M.Pharm) in ‘Clinical Pharmacy and Pharmacology’.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We have laboratories adorned with state-of-the-art facilities. We do our all-out efforts to equip our students skilled and competent to face the challenges of the current healthcare system. We desire to have materialized our dream through providing them with multidisciplinary theoretical courses, laboratory works, project works and intensive industrial training.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Today, our students are engaged in different research works on different fields of Pharmaceutical Science that would improve the outcomes of patients. And their research findings have already come out successfully in different eminent national and international journals. Presently, our students are contributing successfully to the healthcare system both at home and abroad. We are delighted at their glorious professional life. And we are hopeful of their consecutive success and believe they would be able to bring about a breakthrough in healthcare system by dint of their hard labor and strong desire for changes in near future.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our campus is adorned with charming natural beauty that favors an excellent environment for learning. We hope you will find this web site useful to satisfy your queries and also warmly invite you to our campus of natural beauty to learn more about us. And, in case, our web site doesn’t answer your questions fully about our department and its activities, we have stretched our helping hand to you, so feel free to contact us via the mechanisms provided. Thank you for visiting us.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sincerely,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mohammad Salim Hossain, PhD</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chairman</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dept. of Pharmacy</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Noakhali Science and Technology University</p>', 'Chairman\'s Message', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chairmans-message', '', '', '2014-07-13 08:15:11', '2014-07-13 08:15:11', '', '15', 'http://www.nstupharma.org/?page_id=21', '0', 'page', '', '0');
